Add the line below to your .bashrc:

    export ROS_HOSTNAME=192.168.43.CAR_IP
    export ROS_IP=192.168.43.CAR_IP
    export ROS_MASTER_URI=http://192.168.43.PC_IP:11311

open a new terminal and run the script!

    cd /catkin_ws/src/fub_steering_calibration/scripts
    ./calibration.sh
    
Hint:
If the Lidar installed inversed, the steering calibration line 168 should be uncommented and line 170 commented. 

    scripts/angle_calibrator_online.py
